categories: Category:Military personnel of the Sith Empire

nodes.text: Private Leen was a Human male who served in the military of the reconstituted Sith Empire. He was stationed aboard Vaiken Spacedock during the Cold War between the Galactic Republic and the Empire, where he sold stimulants, medpacs, and a vaccine for the rakghoul plague.

Leen had green eyes and fair skin. He wore the grey cap and uniform commonly worn by Imperial personnel, with a belt and gloves. On his tunic was a rank insignia plaque that had eight squares; four blue, two red, and two yellow.
